Algorithm
===============
1.  pwr_state == on;
2. Send(pwr_state);
3. Send(rdy_cmd)
4. fngr_mod begins;
5. if fingerprint detected, send( fngr_value). //Sending fingerprint value
6. if receive(auth)==true && auth==true
7. log_status = true;
8. set_opFlag = true; //Switching to operation mode
9. ListeningLoop begins;
10. receive(cmd)==true &&  cmdTable[cmd] == true
11. execute(cmd);
12. if error_state == false
13. send(cmd_rt_val);
14. else send(error_code);
15. return to ListeningLoop;
16. if receive(cmd) == exit
17. exit from the loop 
18. start shutdown procedure
19. Shut system down.

================================================================
Commands
================================================================
1. pwr_on   //Power on commands
2. pwr_off  //Power off
3. rdy      //System ready
4. opn      //Open deck
5. cls      //Close deck
6. slt      

================================================================
CHALLENGES
================================================================
1. Moto selection and controls
